What's the problem in the Protobuf podspec?  If that isn't properly auto inserting the preprocessor symbols down stream, then at first glance, you'll end up with the same problem down stream here also.  i.e. - anyone that depends on grpc's spect will have to propagate the flags again themselves if they expose protos from their interfaces.

Generally speaking, I have to say CocoaPods seems to assume they are the only want things are built, so having some users that don't want the Frameworks like pods does leads to this sort of problem.  :(

@perotinus - fyi
